[Medicoeconomic evaluation of the treatment of morbid obesity by Swedish 
adjustable gastric banding (SAGB)].

[Article in French]

Chevallier JM(1), Daoud F, Szwarcensztein K, Volcot MF, Rupprecht MF.

Author information:
(1)Service chirurgie générale et digestive, hôpital européen Georges-Pompidou, 
